-- Bayer says offer period for Algeta to run until Feb. 24
-- By Ludwig Burger
-- Mon Jan 20, 2014 02:41AM EST
-- None



FRANKFURT, Jan 20 (Reuters) - German drugmaker Bayer <BAYGn.DE> said on Monday the offer period for its agreed bid for Norwegian radiology drug specialist Algeta <ALGETA.OL> would run from Monday until Feb. 24, 0900 local time.

